You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Received
body: On March 17, 2021, we received your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190110982, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
